     UIC Employee Recognition Awards Ceremony and Reception Click here to see this online      UIC Employee Recognition Awards Ceremony and Reception Each November  UIC celebrates Employee Recognition Month  The celebration begins with the Employee Recognition Award Ceremony and Reception  a campus wide event honoring the recipients of the UIC Award of Merit CAPE  Award  and the Janice Watkins Award for Distinguished Civil Service employees  Also recognized are the UI Health Employee of the Year  Physician of the Year  and Resident of the Year awards UIC celebrates years of service for employees beginning with five years  followed then in five year increments  All employees celebrating years of service are honored by their department or unit  Those who have reached                 and    years of service will be honored at the Employee Recognition Ceremony in November Below are important details for the      Employee Recognition Ceremony and Reception  November   m      West Roosevelt Road at the corner of Roosevelt and Halsted http   uicforum uic edu  http   uicforum uic edu  Entrance closest to venue Parking relocation will be honored for any attendee who has a current UIC campus parking permit  which must be displayed at all times   A special flat rate of        will be charged for those who are attending this UIC Forum event Event invitations have been sent to all honorees via university email Please visit the links below to view lists of the      Employee Recognition Award recipients and employees celebrating years of service hr uic edu      EmployeeRecognitionRecipients https   www hr uic edu      EmployeeRecognitionRecipients hr uic edu      ServiceYearList https   www hr uic edu      ServiceYearList For further event information  please visit the UIC Human Resources  Employee Recognition webpage at http   www hr uic edu employee recognition  http   www hr uic edu employee recognition  For questions  contact Rebecca Fortier at rfortier uillinois edu rfortier 